score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a18d8ca8c8435746c25dba507e5ffc2810233a5","tid":2081404,"uid":9554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761e18dd586b706c3febbc739b070bc23e977bc0","tid":2081404,"uid":256215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"有冇飲過酒? 似酒疹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"有啲但以前飲都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"唔會次次有，而且係飲幾十次都未必出一次，睇你飲酒習慣。<br />\n<br />\n如果係冇乜感覺多數係酒疹，安全D睇醫生，或者自己抗過敏藥都可以。正路3到5日唔理佢都會好。"},{"pid":"79fe165ad4197d81956bad99afc4ff86136ee228","tid":2081404,"uid":286881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"白斑似汗斑？<br />\n紅粒粒可能係天氣or濕熱。我背脊/手臂都有啲。試下沖凍水涼。<br />\n臂粒之前睇過皮膚科佢話好多人都係咁就算揸完野過一排又會有"},{"pid":"9c067009c9f009956d6806c9ef6fa3ed31a97f63","tid":2081404,"uid":286881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79fe165ad4197d81956bad99afc4ff86136ee228","tid":2081404,"uid":286881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"白斑似汗斑？<br />\n紅粒粒可能係天氣or濕熱。我背脊/手臂都有啲。試下沖凍水涼。<br />\n臂粒之前睇過皮膚科佢話好多人都係咁就算揸完野過一排又會有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:16:31.000Z","msg":"P.s.我背脊係3,4粒喺頂部，無你咁多。擔心就睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"9320b6a95aed906e808482ccd2f6d7dbbf5a2e24","tid":2081404,"uid":9554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"聽日去睇下普通科先"},{"pid":"db3d39286d9101248c94a4a3530d5ce7e8400874","tid":2081404,"uid":339345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9edf2ac2b424aad88cc9aa64f1f61c5d24e681ff","tid":2081404,"uid":9554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5d7c1128f7dd163fe2dd704db2acf0efebe8784","tid":2081404,"uid":339345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T00:19:54.000Z","msg":"想問樓主背脊啲白斑有冇睇過醫生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:17:04.000Z","msg":"有佢話真菌感染"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:52:47.000